snippet.title: Leave Deana , myself  & Holly outta ya mouth and live streams RSN. Period.
snippet.description:
If you would like to donate to my channel:
PayPal: paypal.me/bomby67
Cash App: $kshell2121
membership link: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOsvFb51lsbNjAH8ANAvMgw/join

Yes, I am in the process of going thru life changes that 
 will affect the rest of my life, donations are always welcome, and are so appreciated. I will eventually be back on top again, just at this time, well, life happens. 

You can email me with any topics or questions  @Bombshellreloaded@gmail.com
When you Join #BomBNation, your part of a family. We laugh, cry, and yell together. key word, together. I have always said, whomever has been mistreated, bullied, felt unwanted, ALL are  welcome here. You'l be a part of a great group of people who support each other, not tear each other down. I've always promoted one love, a melting pot of all sectors where I can have a  open channel  and can have several different sectors in it's chat, and everyone just be there to show love to each other, the channel holder, and support one another. Without my subs, and mods, there is no BombShell. I cannot do it without you all and I grateful to all of you. YUep, Imma Drama Channel, reality Version, I stand up for what's right, even if I have to stand alone. I;m ok with that. You'll either love me or really hate me, either way, you still watching right? :) 
I Will soon have some merchandise for sale, for any who want to become a part of the BombSquad. I am slowly trying to pull my brand together, I do need some help in graphics, intro's what have you, if anyone can help. Thank you all so much from my heart to yours for anything you can help me with.
